widgets.description:
The average queue length of the requests that were issued to the device. It was previously known as Disk I/Os Weighted.
Unit: aqu-sq - dimensionless (number of queued operations)
widgets.title: Average Queue Size (aqu-sz)

promQL.name: A
promQL.query: sum without(state,device) (system_filesystem_usage{state="used",device!~"/dev/loop.*", device!~"tmpfs|nsfs"}) / sum without(state,device) (system_filesystem_usage{device!~"/dev/loop.*", device!~"tmpfs|nsfs"})
